videos.description: Will Richardson swings a pass to Bol Bol, who drains a 3-pointer from well beyond the arc to extend the Ducks' early lead.
videos.headline: Bol swishes deep 3-ball

videos.description: Yauhen Massalski thinks he has a layup at the rim, but Bol Bol reaches over him to pin the shot against the backboard.
videos.headline: Bol uses long wingspan to glass Massalski

videos.description: Payton Pritchard sends one towards the rim, and Kenny Wooten elevates to put it home through contact for the bucket and a foul.
videos.headline: Pritchard lobs to Wooten for and-1 alley-oop

videos.description: Bol Bol takes it away from Isaiah Wright, and Will Richardson goes coast-to-coast for the transition finish.
videos.headline: Bol's steal leads to Richardson's layup

videos.description: Bol Bol launches one from NBA range and gets it to fall, narrowing the San Diego lead to 32-31 with just seconds to go in the first half.
videos.headline: Bol connects on long triple before halftime

videos.description: Bol Bol registers another rejection on Yauhen Massalski, going airborne  and extending to swat away the hook shot.
videos.headline: Bol elevates for 5th block of game
